            <title>[BEAM-619] UnboundedSourceWrapper snapshotting fails with IndexOutOfBoundsException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEAM-619</link>
                <project id="12319527" key="BEAM">Beam</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;UnboundedSourceWrapper&lt;/tt&gt; fails with an &lt;tt&gt;IndexOutOfBoundsException&lt;/tt&gt; when checkpointing is enabled and the parallelism of the operator is greater than 1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The issue lies in the correctness of the local reader/source assignment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
